Online sports betting firm, Betway, has announced the addition of a new product called Win Boost on its platform. The brand will reward customers by boosting their Multi Bet payouts by up to 250 per cent. The new feature offers customers opportunity to increase the payouts on all Multi Bets placed on the platform. To qualify for a boost, bettors will be required to place a Multi Bet, consisting five or more legs, each with odds of 1.2 or more. The more legs added to the betslip, the bigger the boost. Betway Country Manager, Lere Awokoya said: “We are thrilled about the Win Boost offer because it gives bettors the opportunity to boost their Multi Bet winnings by up to 250 per cent. “At Betway, the goal is to make sure that our customers have multiple options when they visit our platform and with the addition of this feature, the odds of winning are much higher.” “To participate in the promo, a player has to log in or register an account through the Betway website or app. Then, create a Multi Bet with five or more selections, each at odds of at least 1.2. The more selections added to the betslip, the bigger the boost.”  Terms and conditions and other detailed information on how to partake in this offer, as well as a step-by-step guide through the game and betting process, can be found on the Betway website at www.betway.com.ng. Betway, Principal sponsors of English Premier League side West Ham United, continues to charm its customers with new and existing features like 4 To Score, Book-a-Bet, Lucky Numbers and more.  